column2: SB Plays The Forgotten City 01 - A Relaxing River Voyage
column7:
I hope I'm not going to regret not taking that gun....

The Forgotten City is a game about a nice trip to Italy, except actually it's some kind of morality play time loop nightmare scenario like a version of Groundhog Day where everybody dies horribly. You know what, I'd probably actually watch that. Bill Murray running down the street screaming while the groundhog just goes totally sickhouse on everyone? Heck yeah. They could call it Punxsutawney Kill. I'd buy ten tickets for that right now.
Get it on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/874260/The_Forgotten_City/
